Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用亚空间航法到地表
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太大胆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我你从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20世纪中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类发现宇宙是由波动而生是移动着的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2046年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类发现人体发出的某种波动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可变换成强力的宇宙能源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个波动在人感动时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起重要的人的时候会增强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之人在专注唱歌时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会产生巨大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类因此将这未知的力量称为歌能源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌为什不回头看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么生气干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌靠的是心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对手不是人我很难进入状况的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们的敌人也不是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌对他们行不行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看花有没有反应就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧我会让这些向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起回头的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 是时空异常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么歌能源探测器会发出这样的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人完全没有动嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太迟钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛我只是差你一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵对那声音产生反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵动了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔这个借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等你想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了就马上给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你打的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想来抢走我们的矿石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担心我抢你们挖的东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 我对那个没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要开枪了你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么他想打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个很旧了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手不准你碰它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,满是灰尘的银色吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别惊慌这里很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他一吼肯定又要发生不祥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于有懂事的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安  BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 我的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想挖的巴鲁纳吉姆矿石  可能已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都挖了20年了挖到的全是些化石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里以前都是绿地是个暖和的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的以前2000年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是诅咒之声害的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从开始有那个以后就事件不断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然 果然呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球有怪物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼盖尔爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁敢唱!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢作怪的话 我不会放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子在这星球出生后一直没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从他的父亲死后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就迷上银河网路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他爷爷讨厌音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他喜欢音乐的程度不下于他父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫恰恰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说那个吉他是恰恰的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人随时可能攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:10:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨拉却一点自觉也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实很伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过巴萨拉是有野性直觉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那神秘的声音说不定真有什么秘密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他的野性直觉令人困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他应该稍微有点理性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 各位 要亚空间航行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大雪 吠叫 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸死掉的诅咒之山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知你爸为何死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不是它害的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是它害的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER  我的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,种子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,种子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰在冰中找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是电视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是歌能源探测器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒魔怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞到你的心啦?这不是诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它可不是泛泛之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该在这个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是从时空的扭曲 计算出来的座标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点误差但是也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以巴萨拉的个性迟早会唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能 是上次那个声音先传出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反应点呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那个星球的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就有找等于没找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相当的混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,视野太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不见 看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩多罗 坐稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那个打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 不能太勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那个打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流浪的.....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流浪的杰特拉帝人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是流浪的杰特拉帝人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音是他发出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 雷伊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌声能源探测器 好像\N无法承受能源的急速变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过热了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能在做歌唱大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 查出地点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该在那颗星球的反面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是应该?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER.....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时乖乖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要坐 BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能让你坐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在起要来真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我的歌吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱的好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小的人类有这么大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔NSP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感测到异常的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔NSP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感测到异常的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦之火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 盖佩尔尼奇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  我知道梦之火焰的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是不合我的梦的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把他抹杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纳塔尼巴尔肯已调整完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去测试性能吧 是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟格拉比尔一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候看过林明美的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是很怪的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么小人类女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用歌声阻止了  我们杰特拉帝人的大舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问爸妈这不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们却说是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有林明美这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对要成为不输给林明美的厉害歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是你就到这里练歌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在人多的城市  无法大声唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里对着雪山  做发声练习罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是件好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过银河很大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为自己练得很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却遇上你这样的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我输给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌是没有胜负的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不就够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞你的心?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你也直撞我的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好巨大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.53,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普罗多戴比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普罗多戴比尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 是很强的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.27,0:24:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了你要乖乖躲在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.52,0:24:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.39,0:24:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是异常灵魂的真面目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.27,0:24:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死它 它一点也不美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.41,0:24:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.75,0:25:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打死你!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.79,0:25:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然之美  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.30,0:25:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞弹太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.00,0:25:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是为了这种事修行的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.47,0:25:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.71,0:25:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.61,0:25:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种灵魂...怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好响亮阿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.50,0:25:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他居然用歌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.70,0:25:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的只用歌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.40,0:25:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.30,0:25:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER  我也要上去 FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.67,0:25:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER  我也要上去FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.81,0:25:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER  我也要上去FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.64,0:26:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这种事!? 这就是歌的力量吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.51,0:26:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这种事!? 这就是歌的力量吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.02,0:26:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩多罗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.49,0:26:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的声波对那家伙行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.46,0:26:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波长已经调整过
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.33,0:26:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的改造美
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.41,0:26:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.30,0:26:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得已使用禁忌绝招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.60,0:26:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合体
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.25,0:27:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三合一
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.15,0:27:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你们无法使用歌打倒我了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.22,0:27:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.36,0:27:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.54,0:27:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.07,0:27:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了 洪水来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.01,0:27:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大洪水
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.31,0:27:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来自诅咒之山
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.75,0:27:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩多罗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.09,0:27:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过 声波不再有效果啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.20,0:28:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.90,0:28:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼盖尔爷爷你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.57,0:28:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我死也不走
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.04,0:28:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别固执了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.38,0:28:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 玛露卡丽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.01,0:28:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要等到佩多罗回来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.55,0:28:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.34,0:28:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.21,0:28:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.08,0:28:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米莲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.11,0:28:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米莲?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.19,0:28:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米莲  设定打开声音扩大器
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.92,0:29:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.19,0:29:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.06,0:29:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.54,0:29:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.91,0:29:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 我快裂开了!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.16,0:29:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差异太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.13,0:29:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.77,0:29:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行三合一的限制到了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.34,0:29:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样 用突击之美
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.65,0:30:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要撞上山了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.79,0:30:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要撞上去  这是引退之美
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.97,0:30:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.15,0:30:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱米莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.19,0:30:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.50,0:30:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱米莉亚 爱米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.44,0:30:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱米莉亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.74,0:30:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.48,0:31:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧? 爱米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.02,0:31:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是喝了点水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.92,0:31:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻  太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.09,0:31:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌的力量好厉害唷
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.99,0:31:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.96,0:31:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过...其实
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.03,0:31:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想把自己的心  也传给他们懂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.27,0:31:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.04,0:31:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,种子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.04,0:31:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.44,0:31:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩多罗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.81,0:31:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰的种子 看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.51,0:31:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.95,0:31:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信 埋在冰理两千的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.85,0:31:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银河宇宙种子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.72,0:31:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发芽了!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.52,0:31:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估计是歌的力量造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.56,0:31:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.56,0:31:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌有那种力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.76,0:31:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.50,0:31:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:31:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 米莲
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.47,0:32:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.37,0:32:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.43,0:32:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.63,0:32:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的歌太难懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,紫色的全景画 银河的高速路 默默注视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,便能 敲击我的心房 SHOOTING STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不夜之城 与我不断加速的心跳重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔向着未知的明天祈祷之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所听到的 那动听旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那不可思议的歌声将我紧紧拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我 SEVENTH MOON 这心中的迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,将会引领我去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,苍蓝摇曳的 SEVENTH MOON 在回荡的旋律之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有沉醉于舞步 去不断寻找答案一途
